1) Passport to World Band Radio

2) Cumbre DX, Hans Johnson in particular

3) Electronic DX Press, Bob Padula in particular

Listeners/readers who notice any other infractions are urged to contact us. Should any of the above wish to start cooperating and be removed from this embarrassing list, we would welcome them. We draw circles to include everyone; they draw circles of exclusion. This is not an ``enemies list`` -- I want to be a friend; why don`t they? IF YOU FIND OUR SHARING OF THIS INFORMATION HELPFUL, PLEASE CONSIDER MAKING A REGULAR DONATION TO SUPPORT OUR WORK HERE AND ON WORLD OF RADIO. THANK YOU! GLENN HAUSER, BOX 1684, ENID, OK 73702, USA
